%% dashAI — Violation lifecycle state machine
%% Grounded in lib/violations/engine.ts (debounce/MIN_TRACK_AGE), lib/evidence/store.ts (IndexedDB),
%% app/api/seal (sealed) + app/api/report (reported) + /verify (verified).
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Detected
    Detected: Detected (kandidat)\nObjek/track terlihat di frame\n(coco-ssd + IoU tracker)
    Detected --> Detected: track age < MIN_TRACK_AGE (4)\natau di dalam debounce (6 dtk)
    Detected --> Confirmed: aturan lolos + age >= 4\n+ debounce lewat
    Detected --> [*]: track hilang / noise\n(cos flow tak terpenuhi)

    Confirmed: Confirmed\nViolationCandidate (confidence 0..1)\n+ snapshot pasal UU 22/2009
    Confirmed --> StoredLocal: saveEvent()

    StoredLocal: Stored (lokal)\nIndexedDB di perangkat\n(privacy-by-design)
    StoredLocal --> Sealed: pengguna setujui →\nPOST /api/seal
    StoredLocal --> [*]: pengguna hapus (deleteEvent)

    Sealed: Sealed (server)\nsealedAt + payloadHash +\ntanda tangan Ed25519
    Sealed --> Reported: POST /api/report\n(verifySealed dulu)

    Reported: Reported\nPDF tilang/kecelakaan/coaching\n+ QR ke /verify
    Reported --> Verified: verifikator cek\nhash + signature

    Verified: Verified\nVALID (utuh) atau DIUBAH\n(tamper-evident)
    Verified --> [*]
